        <node TEXT="又称持久型XSS，比反射型XSS更具有威胁性，并且可能影响到Web服务器自身的安全。攻击脚本将被永久的存放在目标服务器的数据库或文件中。常见注入点论坛、博客、留言板、网站的留言、评论、日志等交互处。攻击方式攻击者在发帖或留言的过程中，将恶意脚本连同正常信息一起注入到发布内容中。随着发布内容被服务器存储下来，恶意脚本也将永久的存放到服务器的后端存储器中。当其他用户浏览这个被注入了  恶意脚本的帖子时，恶意脚本就会在用户的浏览器中得到执行。" ID="e00wVlsi6e" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%88%E7%A7%B0%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85%E5%9E%8BXSS%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%94%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E5%9E%8BXSS%E6%9B%B4%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%A8%81%E8%83%81%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%88%B0Web%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%82%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E6%88%96%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E7%82%B9%E8%AE%BA%E5%9D%9B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%81%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E6%9D%BF%E3%80%81%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E7%9A%84%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E3%80%81%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E5%A4%84%E3%80%82%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%96%E6%88%96%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%BF%9E%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%A2%AB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%86%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82%E5%BD%93%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E4%BA%86%20%20%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%96%E5%AD%90%E6%97%B6%EF%